  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/CryptoTokenKit\/TKError\/Code\/badParameter\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T13:37:43Z\n---\n\n# TKError.Code.badParameter\n\n**Case**\n\nAn invalid parameter was provided.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\ncase badParameter\n```\n\n## Error Codes\n\n- **TKError.Code.notImplemented**: The functionality is not implemented.\n- **TKError.Code.communicationError**: A communication error occurred.\n- **TKError.Code.corruptedData**: The data was corrupted.\n- **TKError.Code.canceledByUser**: The operation was canceled by the user.\n- **TKError.Code.authenticationFailed**: Authentication failed.\n- **TKError.Code.objectNotFound**: The object was not found.\n- **TKError.Code.tokenNotFound**: The token was not found.\n- **TKError.Code.authenticationNeeded**: Authentication is needed.\n- **TKErrorAuthenticationFailed**\n- **TKErrorObjectNotFound**\n- **TKErrorTokenNotFound**\n\n",
